{"tid":1349851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[19] 林鄭月娥鋌而走險，與新界黑社會結成執政同盟","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:12:57.000Z","uid":51620,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fa2cb2bb5b784ac7cd6030ec3c335c30f39ca15","tid":1349851,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978/2846219212117250/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.288915521180978%2F2846219212117250%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=c7be4bcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.288915521180978/2846219212117250/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n【智‧謀】<br />\n林鄭月娥鋌而走險，與新界黑社會結成執政同盟，響應香港經濟日報副社長兼投資專家石鏡泉呼籲，動用籐條和「水喉通」在元朗無差別暴打香港市民。警方完全袖手不管。此舉無疑是向香港宣戰。<br />\n<br />\n因為不論西環曾經發生過什麼樣的刑事毁壞，另一段的元朗，西鐵乘客，不一定穿黑色衫的必是曾去過港島的示威者。林鄭特區政府掀起鄉黑之白色恐怖主義，隨時搞出人命，濫殺無辜。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭這一招，無疑是「盡地一鋪」之最後豪賭，蓄意煽動民間「以暴易暴」，繼「七一」之後，再次企圖激發中國國家主席習近平以中央軍委主席的身份簽署軍令，宣布香港進入緊急狀態，由解放軍出動「平亂」，將中國高層扯進去，以掩蓋其當初提出逃犯修訂法之大錯。<br />\n<br />\n這一手有如偷襲珍珠港。<br />\n<br />\n元朗淪為「匪區」，是對「沙田城市廣場之戰」的戰爭報復，一時消息滿天飛，有愛國勢力警告：今晚「鄉黑」將進襲新界西，格殺勿論。大陸法西斯五毛網民則全線鼓動，配合林鄭，企圖掀起更大的血洗和恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n不論真假，既然香港特區警方已經無意執法維持起碼的治安，局面極為艱鉅，請港九新界各區市民，務必首先注意安全。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭果然「官到無求膽自大」，與其個人絕境無路，不如全港玉石俱焚。其間全香港公務員包括警隊，多年建立的形象，毀於一炬。<br />\n<br />\n面對一個瘋婦及其少數追隨者，全港各界，此刻必須團結，穩站在人類文明的一方，以智謀捍衛一百六十年的基業的香港。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：路透社"},{"pid":"07576ccbaf908f2363bd4cf7208c5d17e901debe","tid":1349851,"uid":51620,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nr74EfB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNr74EfB.gif&h=a8b64861&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"663b8a19cd5f6bdc00d4794f4ab8c1dfd29bfcf0","tid":1349851,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"佢地鍾意FF幻想港獨<br />\n由佢啦<br />\n<br />\n科威特亡國後都唔叫獨立啦<br />\n死中囯國人只識自瀆"},{"pid":"a31a039f3efa1b037c9de1f018f8b1204b6d5ba7","tid":1349851,"uid":268431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c1cc417337ab458d361a5f1611840500de1fb5","tid":1349851,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca97170924fb46b44db28f0112c6b335959f2a5e","tid":1349851,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"我宣布「政警鄉黑」大合作，「黑警、黑鄉、黑社會」合稱「三黑」，必須追究「三黑」暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46f7111476f3ff3d04970ccc3fcea06be130074a","tid":1349851,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"1f7d258b3f579f55abba606a56a0fa3387519212","tid":1349851,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%